{
  "stem": "9943.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the, the Jews-- the Jews were not given their cadavers so easily for such things because there was the-- there was always this Chevra Kadisha, or whatever they are called, that were picking up somebody who died and, and, and buried them.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was their explanation.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So, in other words, they gave us little babies to cut.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I know the first day, I didn't go to, to this prosectorium.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was afraid.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "At that time, the whole idea of cutting a cadaver was not such a, a thing that one was looking forward to do.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then I went to the prosectorium.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And [POINTING] I got a little baby like that size.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] well, of course, it, it upset me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It upset me so that when I make tea in the evening in this El Dorado, and the, the kettle was singing, it, it was like, for me, as if the child is crying-- I mean, in my imagination.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But again, you had-- you had to do it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You had to do it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But this-- the, the Polish students had the [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] big cadavers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we, the, the Jews, had to have-- that was the only thing that I felt.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At the examination-- the examination for this-- the application to medical school, I just didn't say anything about it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] there were for 20 seats or 20-something that they accepted Jews, there were over 400 people that applied to, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to that examination.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
